Version 0.3.0 (2017-08-25)
--------------------------

Bug Fixes
~~~~~~~~~

* exit carbon if any task raises an exception
* host object does not contain container name
* add retry function to docker_inventory script
* **providers.beaker:** beaker provision not handling exception from ansible or container.
* **providers.beaker:** make beaker xml file name unique
* **providers.beaker:** adds beaker job url and cleanup logging
* **providers.openstack:** catch all exceptions that may be raised by openstack client
* **providers.openstack:** penstack node building exceeding timeout limit


Features
~~~~~~~~

* **core:** run carbon tasks concurrently
* **signals:** add signal generators
* **cli:** add templating for framework scenario description

Documentation
~~~~~~~~~~~~~

* add message guidelines

Style
~~~~~

* update openstack urls and tenant ids
* follow the standard naming convention for carbon exceptions
* missing import for provisioner integration tests
* organize imports for the entire project

Refactor
~~~~~~~~

* remove additional code taken from Flask
* remove config and compat from code base
* remove unused code and keys from beaker provisioner

Test
~~~~

* fix carbon issue with randomly failing tests

Chore
~~~~~

* set new minimum version for blaster package
* update OS descriptors to reflect updated floating ip pool for OSP10
* add the jenkins job yaml for our nightly tests
* do not start containers when provisioner class is instantiated
* ignore data created by local tests
* use click built-in function to display program version
* include dockerfile for linchpin

